import React from 'react'
import { Row,Container,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
const SeccionImagenes = () => {
  return ( 
        <section className='imgCont '>
            <Container fluid>
                <Col className='col'>
                    <Row>1 of 1</Row>
                </Col>
            </Container>
        </section> 
  )
}

export default SeccionImagenes
